q: A car travels at 22 km/h for 10 minutes. (1 km = 1000 m) What is the distance in meters?
exp: Convert speed: 22 km/h = 6.11 m/s. Time = 10 min = 600 s. Distance = speed × time = 6.11×600 ≈ 3667 m.
